com.incadencecorp.coalesce.framework

Class CoalesceFramework

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.incadencecorp.coalesce.framework.CoalesceFramework
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ICoalesceExecutorService, Closeable, AutoCloseable

    public class CoalesceFramework
extends Object
implements ICoalesceExecutorService, Closeable
    Application using Coalesce should access the persistor (database) through CoalesceFramework.
